{"type":"message","id":"5323d752","parentId":"aa2c8c96","timestamp":"2026-06-13T01:58:27.511Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"b5b0c8eb55f848118d051a41eb431196","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OpenClaw 2026.6.5 (5181e4f) — All your chats, one OpenClaw.\n\nUsage: openclaw mcp add [options] <name>\n\nAdd one MCP server from flags and probe it before saving\n\nArguments:\n  name                               MCP server name\n\nOptions:\n  --arg <value>                      Repeatable stdio argument (default: [])\n  --auth <mode>                      HTTP auth mode: oauth\n  --client-cert <path>               HTTP mutual TLS client certificate path\n  --client-key <path>                HTTP mutual TLS client key path\n  --command <command>                Stdio command to spawn\n  --connect-timeout <seconds>        Connection timeout in seconds\n  --cwd <path>                       Working directory for stdio server\n  --disabled                         Save the server disabled (default: false)\n  --env <key=value>                  Repeatable stdio environment entry\n                                     (default: [])\n  --exclude <csv>                    Comma-separated MCP tool names or '*' globs\n                                     to hide\n  -h, --help                         Display help for command\n  --header <key=value>               Repeatable HTTP header (default: [])\n  --include <csv>                    Comma-separated MCP tool names or '*' globs\n                                     to expose\n  --no-probe                         Save without connecting first\n  --oauth-client-metadata-url <url>  OAuth client metadata URL\n  --oauth-redirect-url <url>         OAuth redirect URL\n  --oauth-scope <scope>              OAuth scope\n  --parallel                         Mark this server safe for concurrent tool\n                                     calls\n  --ssl-verify <boolean>             Verify HTTPS certificates: true or false\n  --timeout <seconds>                Per-request timeout in seconds\n  --transport <type>                 HTTP transport: streamable-http or sse\n  --url <url>                        HTTP MCP server URL"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":4592,"aggregated":"OpenClaw 2026.6.5 (5181e4f) — All your chats, one OpenClaw.\n\nUsage: openclaw mcp add [options] <name>\n\nAdd one MCP server from flags and probe it before saving\n\nArguments:\n  name                               MCP server name\n\nOptions:\n  --arg <value>                      Repeatable stdio argument (default: [])\n  --auth <mode>                      HTTP auth mode: oauth\n  --client-cert <path>               HTTP mutual TLS client certificate path\n  --client-key <path>                HTTP mutual TLS client key path\n  --command <command>                Stdio command to spawn\n  --connect-timeout <seconds>        Connection timeout in seconds\n  --cwd <path>                       Working directory for stdio server\n  --disabled                         Save the server disabled (default: false)\n  --env <key=value>                  Repeatable stdio environment entry\n                                     (default: [])\n  --exclude <csv>                    Comma-separated MCP tool names or '*' globs\n                                     to hide\n  -h, --help                         Display help for command\n  --header <key=value>               Repeatable HTTP header (default: [])\n  --include <csv>                    Comma-separated MCP tool names or '*' globs\n                                     to expose\n  --no-probe                         Save without connecting first\n  --oauth-client-metadata-url <url>  OAuth client metadata URL\n  --oauth-redirect-url <url>         OAuth redirect URL\n  --oauth-scope <scope>              OAuth scope\n  --parallel                         Mark this server safe for concurrent tool\n                                     calls\n  --ssl-verify <boolean>             Verify HTTPS certificates: true or false\n  --timeout <seconds>                Per-request timeout in seconds\n  --transport <type>                 HTTP transport: streamable-http or sse\n  --url <url>                        HTTP MCP server URL","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1781315907507}}
